      "content": "Wait, now you're saying 75% for direct field ops, but with the logistics and general support added in, it's barely breaking even on actual impact. If I'm going to move $500k more, I need to be able to tell my board that this is a high-impact, lean operation. \n\nCan you give me a definitive, single number for the \"direct impact ratio\"—meaning everything that isn't admin or marketing—just so I can justify this to my team? If that number is going to be significantly lower than 90%, I might need to reconsider. I'm really looking for that efficiency mark before I sign off.",
